LICENSE SCOPE
This repository contains a sample application that demonstrates use of the 
ORMCP MCP server. ORMCP is installed separately (for example, via 
"pip install ormcp-server") and comes with its own LICENSE. ORMCP, in turn,
uses Gilhari (including the 
softwaretree/gilhari Docker image and Gilhari SDK) and the embedded JDX ORM
software.
